  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    The 5 `Task.CompletedTask` no-op methods are technical debt from R-pre-1; per architecture §4.5 "Components NOT to build" — DO NOT fix as real-impl repository; retire instead. Cosmos `audit` (`AuditLogService`) is the canonical reader. State the placement decision + retire rationale in PR description per bff-extensions.md.
